### 1. Postoperative Complications
**Extracted Key Points:**
- **Complications Defined Across Studies:** The appendices list various postoperative complications such as infections (acute kidney injury, catheter-associated blood stream infection), neurocognitive issues (dysfunctions in attention or memory), and systemic responses (e.g., increased white blood cell count).
